originalText.text: From entry to exit of the doctor’s office, my experience was excellent and exceptional, as usual. Dr. Greening has been my doctor for over 15yrs and if I was to move to another state or country, I would do everything in my power to keep her as my doctor! I cannot recommend her highly enough.

originalText.text:
Dr Greening is the best Gynecologist I have ever had as my doctor. She is not only a very seasoned, knowledgeable and well educated doctor, she is kind and compassionate. She is always willing to research information as well as giving you time for any questions you you may have.
She is a unique and rich find.

originalText.text: Dr Greening & team's care has been great but GOOD GRACIOUS is it hard to get an appointment with anyone in the network. To get an annual appointment, as an existing patient, I have to book 6 months out; to see a specialist for something, it took a year+. As great as they've been it's really frustrating to be in this position, esp. as an existing patient. I suppose it speaks to how desired the team is, but this is so disappointing.

originalText.text: It was my first time meeting Dr. Greening this week. I’m am so excited to have found a Dr. who takes the time to know you. She asked many questions about me and my family’s history. I felt very comfortable with her and the office.
